Package com.example.myinventoryapp.ItemManagement

Class Item

java.lang.Object
com.example.myinventoryapp.ItemManagement.Item
All Implemented Interfaces:
android.os.Parcelable
public class Item extends Object implements android.os.Parcelable
Item is the object content item that implements parcelable interface whose instances can be written to and restored from a Parcel - container for a message (data and object references).
